  "texts": [
    "Individual food choices are shaped by cultural backgrounds, exposure to diverse cuisines, and changing health priorities over time.",
    "AI models can incorporate real-time user feedback from mobile apps, meal logging activities, or short taste preference surveys.",
    "These inputs allow the system to learn from user interactions and continuously refine predictions.",
    "This adaptive capability is especially valuable in personalized nutrition programs, where dietary adherence depends heavily on how enjoyable users find the recommended meals.",
    "Integrating genetic, metabolic, and behavioral data into gustatory AI models can greatly enhance prediction accuracy and user satisfaction."
